 \begin{align} 5(1 + 2 + \dots + 20) - 2(1 + 2 + \dots + 20) &= 3 (1 + 2 + \dots + 20) \\ &= 3 \cdot \frac{20 \cdot 21}{2} \\ &= 630. \end{align}
